    bf:summary [ a bf:Summary ;
            rdfs:label "The ATSDR toxicological profile succinctly characterizes the toxicology and adverse health effects information for the toxic substance described therein. Each peer-reviewed profile identifies and reviews the key literature that describes a substance's toxicological properties. This public health statement tells you about phosphate ester flame retardants and the effects of exposure to them."@en ] ;
